column5: Tried to turn on the Humingbird and it wouldn't turn on battery connections are all good and it almost looks like the unit is get some power as it looks like there is a faint light on the screen...last week I was having issues with it not turning off. Wondering if anybody has any idea, may be a good time for a upgrade!
Thats as good an excuse, if there was any.LOL  I have no input as far as the troubles,but I like new toys.
